      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments use the same pump geometry, blood analog fluid, and operating envelope as the COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump using a porcine blood analog at hematocrit 33%. Operating conditions span the full COU envelope (2.5–5 L/min, 2500–3500 RPM). Geometry fidelity was confirmed by CMM measurements of the physical test article against the CAD model."
